'''Weekkata''' was a [[Jawa/Legends|Jawa]] clan. The Weekkata used to patrol the [[Wayfar/Legends|Wayfar]] area of [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] in the time of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. [[Aguilae|Khea Nkuul]] belonged to this clan.

